issue.title: Messenger chatbot: create "continue" button postback handler
issue.body:
- create continuePostbackHandler function

  - modify messageHandler for messages that don't have quick_reply property
  - modify messageHandler for attachment messages
  - add START_SEARCH_YES switch
  - return body.statusMessage if message successfully sent
